result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :width="800"
  :visible="visible"
  :confirmLoading="confirmLoading"
  @ok="handleOk"
  @cancel="handleCancel"
  cancelText="关闭"
>
  <a-spin :spinning="confirmLoading">
    <a-form :form="form">
      <a-form-item :labelCol="labelCol" :wrapperCol="wrapperCol" label="创客达人/大使账号">
        <a-input v-if="autoSubmit" placeholder :disabled="autoSubmit"></a-input>
        <a-auto-complete
          v-else
          class="global-search"
          @select="onSelect"
          @search="handleSearch"
          optionLabelProp="text"
          v-decorator="['userId',{ rules: [{ required: true, message: '请输入账号id' }] }]"
          placeholder="请输入账号id"
          :disabled="autoSubmit"
        >
          <template slot="dataSource">
            <a-select-option
              v-for="item in dataSource"
              :key="item.nickName"
              :text="item.nickName"
              class="selece-option"
            >
              <a-avatar :src="item.header" :srcSet="item.header" style="margin-right: 15px"></a-avatar>
              {{ item.nickName }}
            </a-select-option>
          </template>
          <a-input class="associate_input">
            <a-button
              slot="suffix"
              class="search-btn"
              type="primary"
              size="large"
              @click="beginSearch"
            >
              <a-icon type="search"></a-icon>
            </a-button>
          </a-input>
        </a-auto-complete>
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item :labelCol="labelCol" :wrapperCol="wrapperCol" label="被邀请人id">
        <a-input v-if="autoSubmit" placeholder :disabled="autoSubmit" :value="invitedUserId" />
        <a-auto-complete
          v-else
          class="global-search"
          @select="onSelect1"
          @search="handleSearch"
          optionLabelProp="text"
          v-decorator="['invitedUserId',{ rules: [{ required: true, message: '请输入被邀请人id' }] }]"
          placeholder="请输入被邀请人id"
          :disabled="autoSubmit"
        >
          <template slot="dataSource">
            <a-select-option
              v-for="item in dataSource"
              :key="item.nickName"
              :text="item.nickName"
              class="selece-option"
            >
              <a-avatar :src="item.header" :srcSet="item.header" style="margin-right: 15px"></a-avatar>
              {{ item.nickName }}
            </a-select-option>
          </template>
          <a-input class="associate_input">
            <a-button
              slot="suffix"
              class="search-btn"
              type="primary"
              size="large"
              @click="beginSearch"
            >
              <a-icon type="search"></a-icon>
            </a-button>
          </a-input>
        </a-auto-complete>
      </a-form-item>
    </a-form>
  </a-spin>
</a-modal>
